org.kepler.objectmanager.cache

Class WorkflowRunCacheObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kepler.objectmanager.cache.CacheObject
      • org.kepler.objectmanager.cache.WorkflowRunCacheObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, CacheObjectInterface

    public class WorkflowRunCacheObject
extends CacheObject
implements java.io.Externalizable
    Class that represents an object in the CacheManager. This class should be extended by each type of object that wants to control its own lifecycle events and serialization events.
    See Also:
